Author: Ben McGahee
Title:  Bouncy Balls
Date: 2/27/2016
Purpose:  This HTML/CSS/JavaScript animation shows a red, green, and black bouncy balls bouncing 
off the walls and colliding into each other.  The application displays the total number of collisions
during the animation.
Note:  The CSS code for ballstyle.css and JavaScript code for bouncyballs.js are presented in separate files.

<!DOCTYPE html>
   <head>
     <meta charset = "utf-8" />
     <link rel = "stylesheet" href = "ballstyle.css">
     <title>Bouncy Ball</title>
   </head>
   <body>
      <h1 id = "balls">Bouncy Balls!</h1>
      <canvas id = "space" width = "300" height = "500"></canvas>
      <script language = "JavaScript" src = "bouncyballs.js"></script>
   </body>
</html>
